title: Entrepreneurship competition coming to Manchester
text:
MANCHESTER, N.H. (AP) - An effort to promote entrepreneurship is coming to Manchester.
The "Rise of the Rest" is visiting the city to work closely with people in startup businesses.
Manchester on Thursday is the fourth stop of a five-city tour that includes Baltimore, Philadelphia, Buffalo and Portland, Maine.
Entrepreneurs try to come up with their best pitch as they compete for investors.
